snippet.title: Harry Potter and the Chamber of Secrets UK DVD (2003) Forbidden Forest Challenge Game
snippet.description: In this game, drive through the forbidden forest and find the way out of the forest and back to Hogwarts and remember that choosing the right turns correctly gets you back safely where as 3 mistakes/wrong answers ends the game.
